      <section id="introduction">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <p>
          Welcome to Namaste India! We are dedicated tohelping travelers from
          around the world immerse themselves in the rich tapestry of Indian
          culture, history, and cuisine. Our mission is to bridge the gap
          between visitors and the vibrant heritage of India, making your
          journey not just a visit, but a memorable experience..
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- 4. What You Offer -->
      <section id="offerings">
        <h2>What We Offer</h2>
        <p>
          At Namaste India, we provide a wealth of resources to help you
          navigate your journey through India. Here’s what you can expect:
          Cultural Insights: Learn about the diverse traditions, festivals, and
          customs that make India unique. From the colorful celebrations of
          Diwali to the serene rituals of yoga, we cover it all. Historical
          Context: Dive into the rich history of India, exploring ancient
          civilizations, architectural marvels, and the stories that have shaped
          our nation. Discover the significance of landmarks like the Taj Mahal
          and the forts of Rajasthan. Culinary Adventures: Experience the
          flavors of India through our curated guides on regional cuisines. From
          the spicy curries of the South to the delectable sweets of the North,
          we’ll help you navigate the culinary landscape and even share some
          recipes to try at home! Travel Tips: Get practical advice on traveling
          in India, including must-visit destinations, local etiquette, and tips
          for navigating the vibrant streets of our cities.
        </p>
